metadata.name: The Europa House
metadata.description:
"The Europa House"
A Genesis project by ArchitectureofMetaverse.com

The inspiration is from one of the icy moons of Jupiter - Europa.
Jupiter is the largest planet in our solar system and has about 79 moons!
One of its largest moons is “Europa” with an icy surface and gases surrounding it. The Architect’s imagination makes Europa a place to design a dream abode.

The House is fully designed inside and out so that it can be of actual utility once Metaverse is live. A walk-through of the Digital Building along with the soothing eastern "Om" chants can be seen here. 

After the successful purchase of the NFT, The original 3D File of the House will be shared with the buyer upon request which can be later used to integrate with the Metaverse. So this is an art in which one can live.

The Europa House while blending with its surroundings overlooks the magnificent Jupiter in the sky.

(Designed by Architect Sujan Setty, Founder of Furgonomics.)
